                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Hold, traveler. This artery is under a Company transit levy. Every wagon that rolls owes tonnage, and every set of boots counts as a small wagon."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The road has a grade now. So does everyone on it. Refuse the levy and we settle it the hard way, or step off the straight and we forget you."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Unlicensed transit on a Company artery. Pay the levy, object and become an incident, or walk off the road and out of the ledger."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Operative - the levy",
                    Label: "caravan_hail"
                },
